Enum EventType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EventType>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public enum EventType
extends Enum<EventType>
    Indicates the type of an Event.

      The Event represents the SecuritySchema being created.
      SET_AMENDED_EVENT
      The Event represents the set owned by an Entity being amended.
